                            during his stay in <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2991Eritre">Eritrea</placeName>
                            (<date notBefore="1899" notAfter="1903">1899–1903</date>) or sent to him after his return to Europe.</provenance>
                        <acquisition>The manuscript passed into the possession of the library in <date when="1950">1950</date>, following Conti Rossini’s death in <date when="1949">1949</date> 
